Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.70,0:00:06.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Open your mind. Open your mind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.58,0:00:22.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Far beyond the deep blue Earth,\nyou and I shall meet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.79,0:00:24.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...as a gentle breeze goes by.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.16,0:00:28.16,AMG TITLE,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,AH! MY GODDESS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.16,0:00:29.63,AMG TITLE,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,AH! MY GODDESS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.63,0:00:36.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A snow-white feather will come\nfluttering down, swaying gently in the air.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.77,0:00:43.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Without holding back, I want to\nenvelope you, my one and only love.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.88,0:00:53.29,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know I have the power to protect\nthe one I love, right here in my hands.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.29,0:01:00.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Open your mind.\NJust as I've always dreamed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.03,0:01:06.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let the wind carry off\nyour hopes, faraway.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.93,0:01:13.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have wings nobody can see.\NLook, you have them, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.71,0:01:22.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They'll take us to where we can be free.\NAnyone can be free.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.01,0:01:26.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The sky is so blue...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.40,0:01:39.30,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Something's going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.30,0:01:42.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try to pinpoint the cause\nas soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.83,0:01:45.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true that the System crashed?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.64,0:01:47.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it seems like it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.74,0:01:51.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you have to admit it\nwas an impossible contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.61,0:01:56.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The System's to blame for\napproving a contract like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.92,0:01:59.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How dare he keep\nmy big sister all to himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.79,0:02:02.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll go down there\nand check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.45,0:02:04.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I'm going with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.36,0:02:07.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You'll stay right here and\nwork on fixing the System.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.53,0:02:08.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.26,0:02:12.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But if you go without permission,\nyou'll get punished by the Almighty...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.60,0:02:16.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, I think I'll be on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.97,0:02:24.43,AMG episode name,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ah! Can You Pass the Love Test\NWith Those Low Scores?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.65,0:02:29.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's gotten a lot warmer,\ndon't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.48,0:02:31.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it has.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.65,0:02:36.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're still sneezing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.46,0:02:40.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I've never experienced\nanything like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.76,0:02:43.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's because you're not\nused to the environment...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.93,0:02:46.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.47,0:02:49.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.13,0:02:51.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I think you'd better go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.17,0:02:54.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But we're not finished\nwith our shopping...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.14,0:02:56.34,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I'll take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.34,0:02:59.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You go on home and get\nsome rest, Belldandy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.65,0:03:03.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I think I will then. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.62,0:03:08.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... what about the System Force?\NDo you think it'll kick in?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.39,0:03:10.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.62,0:03:13.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, lately the System Force...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.23,0:03:25.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, today's your day to rest up\nat home, Belldandy. All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.87,0:03:28.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.68,0:03:35.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kanazawa Pharmacy{\i0}\NExcuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.11,0:03:37.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.58,0:03:39.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And what can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.92,0:03:44.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... um... do you have anything\nthat will take care of sneezing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.12,0:03:49.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,For that ailment, I'd recommend\nthese two remedies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.06,0:03:51.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are these safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.36,0:03:55.30,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me? Give her these, and\nshe'll fall head over heels for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.30,0:03:57.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know it's for a she?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.67,0:04:02.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But, there's more! Buy now, and I'll even\nthrow in this special video as a bonus.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.71,0:04:03.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Video?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.91,0:04:07.28,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just watch this tape, and all your\nanxieties will disappear at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.28,0:04:10.02,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's packed with\npractical advice, you see!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.02,0:04:10.95,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.95,0:04:13.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll take those, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.75,0:04:16.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We appreciate your patronage!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.30,0:04:27.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.07,0:04:29.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.07,0:04:33.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I got you something that should\nat least help with your sneezing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.21,0:04:35.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.27,0:04:38.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I think you should take those\nand go rest in your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.48,0:04:39.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to trouble you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.78,0:04:40.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's no trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.88,0:04:44.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I just want you to always be\nin good health, Belldandy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.35,0:04:45.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.79,0:04:50.29,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, so don't push\nyourself too hard, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.29,0:04:51.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.70,0:05:02.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah... I wonder what\nthat video's about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.50,0:05:04.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's a Betamax.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.77,0:05:05.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Love Guidance{\i0}\NHey, it's a Betamax.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.81,0:05:11.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.34,0:05:14.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.48,0:05:18.98,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.98,0:05:22.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What I'm going to do in this video is\nshow you, my bashful little viewers...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:26.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...just what techniques you'll need to\nmaster so you can do this and that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.96,0:05:29.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and the other thing, with a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.16,0:05:32.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, you there, the spineless one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.03,0:05:35.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Have you gotten past\nthe kissing stage yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.10,0:05:42.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now, keep in mind that a girl sometimes\nprefers to be wooed aggressively!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.94,0:05:44.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.71,0:05:47.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, this video is way too realistic!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.71,0:05:52.02,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be depressed about your lack of\nheight. It's boldness that makes the man!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.02,0:05:54.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost like she knows me personally!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.82,0:05:58.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then, let me show you how to\ngive her a kiss she'll never forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.66,0:06:01.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget to create\nthe perfect mood for it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.44,0:06:12.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.81,0:06:18.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.97,0:06:20.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.68,0:06:24.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.42,0:06:31.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi, um, about this medicine\nyou brought me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.76,0:06:34.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.19,0:06:35.02,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.02,0:06:37.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Augh...legs popped out of the video...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.53,0:06:38.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keiichi!{\i0}\NAugh...legs popped out of the video...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:39.40,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.40,0:06:40.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Video?{\i0}\NA woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.67,0:06:46.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, I'm going to\ntake a look at your memory...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.04,0:06:51.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Call forth this man's short-term memory\nstreams...play them back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.41,0:06:56.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.92,0:07:01.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Belldandy, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.05,0:07:03.98,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd! I know you're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.98,0:07:05.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.19,0:07:06.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.06,0:07:08.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.49,0:07:11.40,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot, I knew I'd get busted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.40,0:07:13.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're from the pharmacy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.33,0:07:15.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Goddess 2nd Class, Administration,\NLimited License...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.23,0:07:18.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Belldandy's big sister, Urd.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:19.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.47,0:07:20.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,B-Big sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.94,0:07:24.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please! Must you be so\nblown away by my good looks?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.74,0:07:28.08,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.08,0:07:32.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You've noticed how the System Force\nhas been malfunctioning, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.52,0:07:37.12,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. In the last few days, I've\nhad problems with my health as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.12,0:07:38.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Have you figured out why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.82,0:07:39.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.13,0:07:42.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's all your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.76,0:07:45.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to your goddess-monopolization,\nyou've triggered...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.90,0:07:49.30,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...a host of aberrations and now\nthere's a glitch in the System!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.30,0:07:53.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I was just kind of going with\nthe flow when I made that wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.47,0:07:58.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But the fact is, his wish was\nofficially approved by the System.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:02.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All the same, this is totally\nunprecedented, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.25,0:08:05.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is it going to be a problem if\NBelldandy and I stay together?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.48,0:08:09.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it. That's why\nI've come here, to fix things!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.49,0:08:13.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But Urd, that's out of\nyour jurisdiction, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:16.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, I came to help\nmy sweet little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.23,0:08:19.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And I have permission\nfrom the Almighty One.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.56,0:08:22.30,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then I guess it should be all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.30,0:08:25.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But who's running the System?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.17,0:08:27.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the kid's handling all that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.94,0:08:31.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ohhh... man! I hate you, Urd!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.77,0:08:34.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want your wish\nto be invalidated, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.85,0:08:38.28,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not. I'll do anything\nto stop that from happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.28,0:08:41.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I like to hear!\nI'll need you to cooperate with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.55,0:08:42.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.56,0:08:50.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is pretty serious stuff\nwe've gotten ourselves into, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.16,0:08:51.73,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Everything will be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.73,0:08:56.40,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't look it, but my sister is\nactually more powerful than I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.40,0:08:58.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She is, is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.64,0:09:03.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing is, she has a tendency\nto resort to strong-arm tactics at times...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.62,0:09:14.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.35,0:09:16.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I just need to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.72,0:09:17.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.54,0:09:19.95,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,About the System Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:22.12,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.33,0:09:28.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The System Force is part of\na goddess' support system.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.70,0:09:34.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So unless the damage is repaired, it'll\nput more strain on Belldandy's powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.07,0:09:36.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she hasn't been well lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.57,0:09:38.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.61,0:09:42.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She's going to have to return\nto Heaven to regain her powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.51,0:09:45.58,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But you just said\neverything would be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.58,0:09:49.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I also make it clear that\nyour cooperation would be crucial?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.82,0:09:51.12,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My cooperation?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.12,0:09:55.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The aberration I mentioned was\nan error in your personal data.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.06,0:09:57.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's what caused the\NSystem to malfunction.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.66,0:10:01.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But all that can be resolved by\nsending a sample of your DNA to heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.07,0:10:03.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How are we going to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.60,0:10:06.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You have to make physical\ncontact with Belldandy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.77,0:10:09.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That is, you have to kiss her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.17,0:10:10.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.68,0:10:14.28,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shhh! Of course, you-know-what\nwould be more foolproof...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.28,0:10:18.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...but in your case, that would\nbe like asking for the moon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.08,0:10:24.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, all you have to do is kiss her,\nand you two can stay together forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.62,0:10:26.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.96,0:10:28.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.83,0:10:32.10,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just do whatever I say, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.57,0:10:43.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Am I really gonna do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.54,0:10:46.28,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Stop procrastinating, for god's sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.28,0:10:47.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.68,0:10:49.98,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.98,0:10:51.31,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.12,0:10:59.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Keiichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.09,0:11:04.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, uh... I was just wondering\nif your sneezing fits were gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.60,0:11:09.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but Keiichi, your\nface looks rather red.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.23,0:11:12.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? There's nothing wrong with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.34,0:11:18.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.98,0:11:23.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The color of Keiichi's emotions...\nyellow, mixed with red.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.72,0:11:26.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He seems a bit desperate...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.62,0:11:29.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He must be under stress\nbecause of Urd...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.62,0:11:38.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to worry about me.\NBut thank you for your concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.46,0:11:40.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.67,0:11:44.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now's your chance! Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.27,0:11:46.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Belldandy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.81,0:11:50.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Listen... I'd like you to\nclose your eyes for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.44,0:11:51.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.65,0:11:58.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If I do this... if I do this,\nthen Belldandy can stay...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.75,0:12:00.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.39,0:12:03.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No... I've got to take the plunge!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.66,0:12:07.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.39,0:12:12.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, I forgot I left the kettle on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.60,0:12:18.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You little wuss!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.67,0:12:23.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What was I supposed to do just now?\nIt was bad timing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.04,0:12:24.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.91,0:12:28.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously, you need to\nchange your whole mentality.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.78,0:12:33.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,For now, go take a bath so you can\nget yourself properly psyched up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.32,0:12:34.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.17,0:12:52.73,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's all for Belldandy's sake,\nbut still, what a headache...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.67,0:12:54.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.71,0:12:58.34,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there! Why don't\nI scrub your back for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.91,0:13:00.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.78,0:13:02.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't be so shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.78,0:13:07.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you could just learn to be bolder\nin these situations, Keiichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.11,0:13:10.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have much\nexperience with girls, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.88,0:13:12.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just get out of here, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.89,0:13:16.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me? Is this body of mine\nso unattractive to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.59,0:13:18.50,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I never said that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.50,0:13:22.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then what's the big deal?\NYou come out of there now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.07,0:13:24.10,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.97,0:13:27.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Speech Control... start!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.91,0:13:29.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.77,0:13:32.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to scrub your back,\nisn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.68,0:13:35.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I want you to scrub my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.81,0:13:38.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then, come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.39,0:13:42.95,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.95,0:13:44.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.36,0:13:46.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm getting out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.62,0:13:48.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Attaboy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.79,0:13:51.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.06,0:13:55.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you or aren't you...\nmake up your freakin' mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.94,0:13:58.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What was that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.87,0:14:02.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.61,0:14:09.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry, Keiichi, I've brought you\nso much trouble because of Urd.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.15,0:14:13.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But I know Urd's just as\nworried about you as I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.35,0:14:14.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.09,0:14:19.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But the problem is that she will\nstop at nothing to achieve her goals.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.22,0:14:23.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And she gets so caught up in her\nmethods that she forgets her goals.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.93,0:14:26.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I think I know what you mean by that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.23,0:14:31.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There was a time when I fell\nvictim to a demon's poison...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.64,0:14:36.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No healing spell could cure me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.21,0:14:40.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Our only hope is to borrow the power\nof the Blue Dragon Stone of the East.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.75,0:14:43.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But we can't possibly\nmake it back here in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.62,0:14:46.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me. I'll go get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.05,0:14:51.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My sister went straight\nto the Almighty One...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.39,0:14:52.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm borrowing him, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.42,0:14:53.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}See here, you... come back here!{\i0}\nI'm borrowing him, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.42,0:14:54.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}See here, you... come back here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.03,0:15:02.10,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She took Sleipnir, the Almighty One's\neight-legged steed, without permission...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.10,0:15:04.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...to bring back the Blue\NDragon Stone for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.87,0:15:07.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She did something good, then, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.61,0:15:10.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No... it was only good until that point.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.41,0:15:11.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.34,0:15:16.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She became so enraptured with riding\NSleipnir that she rode him nonstop...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.05,0:15:18.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...for three days and three nights.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.05,0:15:20.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,By the time she returned,\nsomeone else had...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.89,0:15:23.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...already brought back\nthe Blue Dragon Stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.26,0:15:28.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I guess she's the complete\nopposite of you, Belldandy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.39,0:15:30.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Like how she bares all her emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.90,0:15:32.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's not exactly true...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.90,0:15:35.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I live life on my own terms,\njust like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.63,0:15:38.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My staying with you, for example...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.18,0:15:45.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.91,0:15:46.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.48,0:15:50.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to be together forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.25,0:15:51.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.22,0:15:56.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't take action now, Belldandy\nwill have to go back to Heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.42,0:15:58.02,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.79,0:16:01.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.06,0:16:02.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.09,0:16:03.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.26,0:16:04.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.20,0:16:10.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.54,0:16:15.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, another bust!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.24,0:16:22.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that I didn't have the chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.95,0:16:26.58,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to get it done tomorrow,\nsomehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.69,0:16:31.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You can't put the moves on Belldandy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.59,0:16:34.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...because you've never known\nthe wonder of a real woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.49,0:16:38.73,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let me help you out with that... to make\nup for what happened in the bathtub.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.73,0:16:41.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're going\nabout this the wrong way...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.37,0:16:45.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're not bold enough.\NGo on, you can have your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.20,0:16:46.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Whaaat?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.67,0:16:48.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez! You're so annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.94,0:16:51.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Put your hands on my chest!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.37,0:16:53.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.74,0:16:56.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But be gentle, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.42,0:17:04.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.16,0:17:06.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.99,0:17:09.29,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.29,0:17:11.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're resisting again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.23,0:17:14.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi, you care about Belldandy,\ndon't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.17,0:17:16.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.83,0:17:20.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you really care that much,\nthen why can't you kiss her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.87,0:17:24.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I have no choice.\NHere, you can have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.44,0:17:27.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.37,0:17:30.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A supplement for what you lack...\nit's medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.92,0:17:34.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure it's all right\nto use measures like these?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.15,0:17:37.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying you don't care\nif she has to go back to Heaven?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.46,0:17:39.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What? No, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.62,0:17:44.08,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then take your pill.\NThere's no other way now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.93,0:17:50.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.64,0:17:57.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That pill is actually a\npower-boost for Speech Control.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.61,0:17:59.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.84,0:18:03.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You are going now, Keiichi,\nto Belldandy's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.64,0:18:08.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go... I'm going to Belldandy's\nroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.99,0:18:15.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy? Do you have a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.23,0:18:17.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.07,0:18:24.34,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let the games begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.34,0:18:27.34,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.34,0:18:31.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy, can I tell you what I wish for?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.38,0:18:32.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.27,0:18:34.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good boy, good boy... let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.77,0:18:36.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.41,0:18:38.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I want you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.62,0:18:41.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi, you've been acting...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.59,0:18:43.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...how should I put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.96,0:18:45.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I want you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.59,0:18:47.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.16,0:18:49.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You got it! Come on, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.80,0:18:54.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.63,0:18:56.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.60,0:18:58.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I want Belldandy...I want Belldandy to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.14,0:19:00.24,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gray and black...that means...{\i0}\nI want Belldandy...I want Belldandy to...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.24,0:19:01.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gray and black...that means...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.34,0:19:05.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I ask for the release of\nthis soul from captivity...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.85,0:19:10.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.37,0:19:12.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.75,0:19:15.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it must've been that pill...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.65,0:19:17.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,See, Urd told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.62,0:19:18.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.75,0:19:22.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The only way to fix the System\nwould be for me to kiss you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.93,0:19:27.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and send a sample of my DNA\nto Heaven. That's what she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.57,0:19:31.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But if it means you won't have\nto go back to Heaven, then I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.64,0:19:33.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd, what's the meaning of all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.81,0:19:36.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you're onto me,\nI'd better come clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.47,0:19:39.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How could you deceive Keiichi?\NWhat an awful thing to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.81,0:19:43.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a minute. You told me\nthat goddesses can't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.55,0:19:48.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, the reason that Urd has a limited\nlicense despite being more powerful...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.32,0:19:52.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...is because she's being penalized\nfor having lied in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.16,0:19:54.69,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is unforgivable, Urd!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.69,0:19:58.10,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me? It's Keiichi's fault\nfor being so damned inept!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.10,0:19:58.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's my fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.70,0:20:00.10,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I went to all this trouble for you!{\i0}\NHuh? It's my fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.10,0:20:01.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I went to all this trouble for you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.43,0:20:04.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your punishment! Lightning bolt!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.67,0:20:06.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.81,0:20:14.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Take that! Take that! Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.81,0:20:19.28,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thunderbolt!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.52,0:20:28.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.19,0:20:29.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.20,0:20:36.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,As if you had a prayer of defeating me\nwith your powers sealed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.13,0:20:40.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I helped you two move to the\nnext level in your relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.44,0:20:44.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But I never dreamed you'd actually\nraise your hand against your big sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.71,0:20:46.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Summoning electricity...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.48,0:20:49.58,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Roll of thunder! O Supreme Ruler\nwho splits the heavenly skies...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.58,0:20:52.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...let your power smite my enemies now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.75,0:20:55.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Look out, Belldandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.05,0:20:56.69,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.69,0:20:59.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sky-splitting Thunder and Lightning\NStrike!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.38,0:21:01.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.43,0:21:05.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.70,0:21:07.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.47,0:21:16.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Did she self-destruct?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.04,0:21:18.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, I think something else happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.21,0:21:26.98,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Here's a message from the Almighty One.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.85,0:21:32.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It has been determined that System\NForce intervention by Urd, Goddess...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.09,0:21:36.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...2nd Class, Administration, Limited\NLicense, has caused the Server to crash.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.83,0:21:39.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.06,0:21:43.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My sister used her powers here\non Earth without permission, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.20,0:21:47.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...apparently that generated\neven more glitches in the System.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.64,0:21:51.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, Urd is hereby forbidden\nto return until further notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.14,0:21:52.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.51,0:21:57.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kei, I brought you some food!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.92,0:21:59.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Coming! Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.92,0:22:00.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoa!{\i0}\NComing! Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.89,0:22:02.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's another one!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.89,0:22:04.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kei, you sneaky thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.72,0:22:06.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, Megumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.06,0:22:08.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That one just barged in...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.59,0:22:09.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, are you going to be that way?{\i0}\NThat one just barged in...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.56,0:22:11.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, are you going to be that way?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.43,0:22:15.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad, I was going to show you\npictures of Belldandy as a little girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.87,0:22:17.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.44,0:22:20.10,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I want to see them too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.38,0:22:38.08,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One day when I woke up...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.79,0:22:49.50,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A day like any other...\nanother one just beginning.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.50,0:22:58.98,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There you are, yawning...\nyour face is still so sleepy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.98,0:23:05.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because each peaceful day\nwe share is a miracle to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.65,0:23:12.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is where my heart\nwill always return...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.25,0:23:15.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Forever...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.11,0:23:21.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's only one thing I wish for.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.03,0:23:27.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I chase after the same dream,\nwherever it may go.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.47,0:23:33.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The love I feel for you\ngives me strength.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.48,0:23:39.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}May tomorrow be as joyful as today...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.72,0:23:44.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's my wish...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.83,0:23:59.24,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The smiles of the goddesses\nshine down on us like sunlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.24,0:24:01.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The Queen's rage is\nlike a tempest unleashed...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.47,0:24:04.24,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and with those furious eyes\nshe investigates our private lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.24,0:24:07.45,AMG next episode name,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Ah! The Queen and\nthe Goddess' Secret
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.45,0:24:10.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Caught in the crossfire of the battle,\nmankind faces destruction!
